data.name: Label4.Text
data.value:
WinPaletter Store can get themes from either online sources (servers\GitHub repositories) or offline folder containing themes in your device.
To edit the source, go to Settings > Store and then select and edit the source as you want.

data.name: Label9.Text
data.value:
When you open Store main page, you can do the following:
- Left click to preview the theme and do other actions.
- Right click to preview the theme immediately without opening it, and then use mouse wheels on the preview to switch modern/classic preview.
